vote.title: An ordinance amending Chapter 42A, “Special Events; Neighborhood Markets; Dallas Street Seats; Dallas Farmers Market Farmers Market; Streetlight Pole Banners,” of the Dallas City Code for the purpose of (1) addition of language to 42A-22 Location of a Neighborhood Market; and (2) extension of the Dallas Street Seats Pilot Program provisions from July 31, 2022 to July 31, 2023 in 42A-28.2 - Financing: No cost consideration to the City (see Fiscal Information)
